-- STXNEWS LATAM-Santander Brasil approves offering of $2.5 bln in notes
-- 
-- Wed Jan 15, 2014 05:20AM EST
-- None



Jan 15 (Reuters) - Banco Santander Brasil SA <SANB11.SA>, the Brazilian subsidiary of Spain's Banco Santander <SAN.MC>, has approved the offering of 6 billion reais ($2.5 billion) worth of notes to be issued on international capital markets, according to a securities filing late on Tuesday.

